                    UMS Style Guide 1.0 (10.06.96)

                      General guidelines for UMS

                            by Ralf Garbade

This document containes the hyperlinks to the general guidelines for
UMS: for the login procedure of applications, for the file name scheme
and for generating report messages.

   This document applies to UMS, version 11 and higher(1).


