Guidelines
**********

The UMS Style Guide consists of three documents:
  1. @{"Login Guide" Link "loginguide.guide/Main"}, standard for starting aplications.

  2. @{"File Name Guide" Link "filenameguide.guide/Main"}, standard on an uniform naming scheme for files,
     directories and software archives.

  3. @{"Report Guide" Link "reportguide.guide/Main"}, standard for generating report messages.


@EndNode

